      "name": "Mesh sensitivity and iterative convergence verification",
      "description": "Three mesh densities (coarse: 4.2 M cells, medium: 11.6 M cells, fine: 28.4 M cells) were evaluated. Grid convergence index (GCI) for the scalar stress integral was 3.1 % between medium and fine meshes. Iterative residuals converged to below 1e-5 for all transport equations. The medium mesh was selected for production runs.",
